--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-08-20)
F: Add support for 'do-not-query-localhost' option (unbound_do_not_query_localhost)
I: Improve documentation

* Version 0.4.2 (2018-07-24)
I: Consolidate default path

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-07-24)
I: Ensure 'root.hints.link' is being removed

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-07-22)
F: Add support for FreeBSD operating system

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-07-01)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-06-22)
B: Remove 'unbound_stub_zone' testing value

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-06-21)
F: Add option 'unbound_stub_zone'
B: Fix position of '@' symbol in 'unbound_interface' parameter
I: Update documentation

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-06-18)
F: Initial release
